faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁依家有錢人好想要高球場啊，人地有需求啊，你做咩逼人用塊扡嚟起樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T14:00:03.000Z","msg":"頂唔順<br />\n低質偷換概念<br />\n有錢人就一定炒樓?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/hkstat/sub/sp150_tc.jsp?tableID=005&amp;ID=0&amp;productType=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.censtatd.gov.hk%2Fhkstat%2Fsub%2Fsp150_tc.jsp%3FtableID%3D005%26ID%3D0%26productType%3D8&d=tvs6FLCP3kzxy%2BifI1j3NfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=f70a93bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/hkstat/sub/sp150_tc.jsp?tableID=005&amp;ID=0&amp;productType=8</a><br />\n呢個係近年自置居所比率<br />\n呢幾年樓價係點係人都知<br />\n點解响咁既情況下仲可以有升有跌唔係只跌不升?<br />\n因為真係有需求佢地需要住又有錢買囉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/511217/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/511217/page/1</a><br />\n唔係我講架<br />\n其他巴打都咁講架<br />\n你收得皮未?<br />\n係咪剩係得炒樓唔住得?<br />\n連登多人有樓定多人去哥爾夫球場呀戇鳩仔?"},{"pid":"d1c1d86ddcbed91352f13081494828c5a03fec30","tid":651612,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T15:11:12.000Z","msg":"其實拆果個球場起樓我覺得無乜用,畢竟北區交通而家已經超負荷,火車嚟緊仲就沙中線減到八卡,出市區果啲路三埋唔夠兩日就撞車,塞到呀媽都唔認得"},{"pid":"367c682321072d3e8d9bfbc942ac6988b93dae06","tid":651612,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T15:18:57.000Z","msg":"一日150, 起咩樓都無我份"},{"pid":"6ec8b34a2d81aef600051a7b14c87ac802e0d23d","tid":651612,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1c1d86ddcbed91352f13081494828c5a03fec30","tid":651612,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T15:11:12.000Z","msg":"其實拆果個球場起樓我覺得無乜用,畢竟北區交通而家已經超負荷,火車嚟緊仲就沙中線減到八卡,出市區果啲路三埋唔夠兩日就撞車,塞到呀媽都唔認得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T15:19: